NULL, NULL, 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/42982/', '[1] "Product Information. Sutent (sunitinib)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group, New York, NY.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[4] "Product Information. Prolia (denosumab)." Amgen USA, Thousand Oaks, CA.[5] "Product Information. Sutent (sunitinib)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group, New York, NY.', 1767365204);
